      "writtenOn": "2017-11-27T20:19:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "linux-amd64 sounds like a host thing, but I’d have expected “sdk” to be a target thing. What’s up here?",
      "revId": "51863c6e7519ff8361676b6dc8b2addcc8546ba8",
